<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ホームへようこそ！</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-pink-100 dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
    <!-- かわいいヘッダー -->
    <div class="relative w-full h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-gradient-to-b from-pink-300 to-pink-100 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white drop-shadow-lg">🎀 ようこそ！ 🎀</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-gray-100 dark:text-gray-300">便利なツールがたくさんあるよ！</p>
        <a href="#tools" class="mt-5 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-pink-500 font-semibold rounded-full shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">スクロールしてね 💕</a>
        <div class="absolute bottom-5 animate-bounce">
            <span class="text-2xl">👇</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ツール一覧 -->
    <div id="tools" class="py-16 px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">🌟 便利ツール一覧 🌟</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">いろんな機能を試してみてね！</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">🔍 検索ツール</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">便利な検索機能</p>
                <a href="#" class="mt-3 inline-block bg-pink-500 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">開く</a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">📂 ファイル管理</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">オンラインでファイルを管理</p>
                <a href="#" class="mt-3 inline-block bg-pink-500 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">開く</a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md text-center">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">📅 スケジュール</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">予定を簡単に管理</p>
                <a href="#" class="mt-3 inline-block bg-pink-500 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">開く</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
